title: 113: Why is Dak Prescott hot, Jared Goff not?
itunes:title: 113: Why is Dak Prescott hot, Jared Goff not?
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks analyze rookie quarterbacks Jared Goff and Dak Prescott heading into the third week of the preseason. The guys also dive into the potential young talent in Tennessee and say farewell to Producer TD.
